Dataflow_FieldFalloffType_Linear: The falloff function will be proportional to x
Dataflow_FieldFalloffType_Inverse: The falloff function will be proportional to 1.0/x
Dataflow_FieldFalloffType_Squared: The falloff function will be proportional to x*x
Dataflow_FieldFalloffType_Logarithmic: The falloff function will be proportional to log(x)
